WEBVTT

00:06.560 --> 00:08.330
I have a theory.alma

00:08.360 --> 00:09.560
We all eat.

00:09.600 --> 00:11.260
We all sleep.

00:11.300 --> 00:14.530
We all dream.

00:21.530 --> 00:22.530
WOMAN:
Manuel?

00:23.900 --> 00:24.860
Can you hear me?

00:27.580 --> 00:30.880
Manuel wake up
Huh?

00:31.910 --> 00:34.080
What?
What are you doing?

00:34.110 --> 00:37.910
What, what, what are...
what are you talking about?

00:37.950 --> 00:41.350
Geez, Manny,
are you all right?

00:41.380 --> 00:43.980
What do you mean?

00:44.010 --> 00:45.950
You wet the bed.

00:51.750 --> 00:54.910
Our dreams reveal us
to ourselves.

00:54.950 --> 00:56.050
The people we are.

00:56.080 --> 00:57.650
Don't just shoot,
you gotta aim it.

00:57.680 --> 00:59.810
So when that site is in
the middle of the clown's mouth,

00:59.850 --> 01:02.250
then you shoot.
Okay, Daddy.

01:02.280 --> 01:04.980
The people we'd like to be.

01:05.010 --> 01:07.350
Whoo! Yeah!

01:07.380 --> 01:09.180
You don't need much.

01:09.210 --> 01:11.350
Just a little push.

01:12.410 --> 01:14.850
Oh, hole in two!

01:14.880 --> 01:15.880
Hey!

01:15.910 --> 01:17.510
Ah, come on, boy!

01:20.780 --> 01:22.110
You guys have fun?

01:22.150 --> 01:24.010
Oh... sure did.

01:24.050 --> 01:25.010
(grunting):
All right.

01:29.410 --> 01:30.610
Here's your deposit.

01:30.650 --> 01:33.080
A lot of people tell me
the game's even more fun

01:33.110 --> 01:35.250
when they bring their own kid,
rather than renting one.

01:35.280 --> 01:37.210
I know. I heard that.

01:37.250 --> 01:39.410
You know how
to get one?

01:39.450 --> 01:41.250
I know people.

01:49.750 --> 01:50.980
(grunting):
Yeah.

01:54.110 --> 01:57.150
(sighing):
Wait a second, will you?

01:57.180 --> 01:58.680
What are you talking about--

01:58.710 --> 02:00.110
"heads blown off"?

02:05.080 --> 02:07.080
Mm... do me a favor,
look around.

02:07.110 --> 02:11.150
Sometimes... a kid will hide
under the bed, in a closet.

02:13.780 --> 02:15.150
All dead.

02:15.180 --> 02:19.750
No, I have no idea
where the mayor is.

02:19.780 --> 02:21.050
It's 5:52 in the morning.

02:21.080 --> 02:23.580
I'm guessing
that he's at home, asleep.

02:23.610 --> 02:26.650
Wait a second,
give me an address.

02:26.680 --> 02:28.680
How many children?

02:32.050 --> 02:34.350
No, don't move anything,
just lock it down.

02:34.380 --> 02:36.110
I'm maybe 35 minutes away.

02:36.150 --> 02:38.550
I'll be right down there.

02:46.580 --> 02:49.110
Some people have dreams
that amaze them...

02:51.280 --> 02:52.450
...and entertain them.

