And then there are my dreams.

03:35.910 --> 03:37.770
Where is your head?

03:37.820 --> 03:42.620
You keep staring at the ceiling
like your mind is somewhere else.

03:44.110 --> 03:46.760
Like your mind is on someone else.

03:48.930 --> 03:56.130
It's rude to pay a woman for her attention

03:56.820 --> 03:58.320
and then not give her any.

03:58.570 --> 04:00.640
MAN:
Speak English.

04:03.340 --> 04:06.010
You want English?

04:06.040 --> 04:08.640
Why'd you come to Indonesia?

04:08.670 --> 04:09.940
Go home to America.

04:13.910 --> 04:15.310
Where are you going?

04:15.340 --> 04:16.440
I'm going
to the airport.

04:16.470 --> 04:17.839
I'm going home.

04:17.870 --> 04:19.769
(scoffs)
I feel
like going home.

04:19.810 --> 04:21.769
You can't do that.

04:21.810 --> 04:24.910
You're intoxicated.

04:24.940 --> 04:26.170
Do you even have a ticket?

04:28.340 --> 04:32.740
Besides...
it's early in the morning.

04:32.770 --> 04:35.770
It's not time for traveling.

04:35.810 --> 04:39.640
It's time to make love.

04:39.670 --> 04:41.340
Keep the change.

05:19.170 --> 05:20.370
What's the matter?

05:20.410 --> 05:22.040
What's going on?

05:22.070 --> 05:24.770
A dream?
Ugh, yeah.

05:26.940 --> 05:29.340
You want to talk
about it?

05:29.370 --> 05:30.670
I don't know.

05:30.710 --> 05:35.010
I'm not sure there's anything
to talk about.

05:35.040 --> 05:36.740
Oh, wow.

05:36.770 --> 05:38.310
Well, that's a first.

05:41.910 --> 05:46.140
I mean,
it took place in Indonesia.

05:46.170 --> 05:48.810
I don't know anyone
in Indonesia.

05:50.340 --> 05:51.540
You would've
liked it, though.

05:51.570 --> 05:53.410
There was a naked
girl in it.

05:58.970 --> 06:01.340
This is weird.

06:01.370 --> 06:03.140
I just had the
exact same dream.

06:03.170 --> 06:05.240
Oh, really.

06:05.270 --> 06:06.570
Truly.

06:06.610 --> 06:11.740
Was there a guy in your dream
who got his head chopped off?

06:11.770 --> 06:13.570
No.

06:13.610 --> 06:15.510
I just had the
naked girl part.

06:15.540 --> 06:17.740
I see.

06:17.770 --> 06:19.210
You had a guy...

06:23.610 --> 06:26.170
Well, I hope you're happy.

06:26.210 --> 06:27.940
Now I'm afraid to
go back to sleep

06:27.970 --> 06:29.110
and finish the dream.

06:29.140 --> 06:31.870
Yeah, well,
welcome to my world.

